column5: THATS IT,,,,,,,,JUST HI.   Took a break from boxing up, for the move.
Just back down to our old place.LOL  Amazing how much crap you/well she   can build up living in a 3 bedroom.LOL
Hey BrianB---Ya Have'nt heard from a guy called Misfish lately have ya?
Yep,he sends his best to ya Bush.  Ok, breaks over,so I have been told. I dont want to be switched.
Had no idea you were a boxer.It makes you hands,arms and elbows hurt when you get old.Road work is your friend.Good luck with the move. Joe

Hi again. The move went well.All hooked up again.   My back and knees are a bit sore. Darn them stairs,but what ya going to do when ya get old,,,,,,,,older.  Were happy with our old/new nest.  Now to get out turkey hunting and get the boat out.   I cant believe what my Colts are doing.WAKE UP BOYS.
